From 18f3fdfde97481e7ee2be2033e051eec356920a1 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: salahmosa531-cmd <salahmosa531-cmd@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Sun, 15 Feb 2026 08:42:30 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] fix: stabilization phase - settings sync, barcode
 reactivity, error handling
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

## Root Causes Addressed

1. **Settings Sync (Admin ↔ Kiosk)**
   - Root cause: Settings cached in memory could become stale across sessions
   - Fix: Added app lifecycle observer to reload settings on foreground resume
   - Added logging tags: [SETTINGS_INIT], [SETTINGS_FOREGROUND], [SETTINGS_RELOAD], [SETTINGS_CHANGED]

2. **Barcode/QR Interval & Disable**
   - Root cause: QR timer not rebuilt when settings changed, used hardcoded AppConstants
   - Fix: Centralized interval reading from SettingsState, timer rebuilds on interval change
   - Added logging tags: [BARCODE_ENABLED], [BARCODE_DISABLED], [BARCODE_INTERVAL_CHANGED]
   - When QR disabled: timer stops, UI hidden, _qrCode set to null

3. **Attendance Screen Reactivity**
   - Root cause: Screen used AppConstants.qrRefreshSeconds instead of current settings
   - Fix: Subscribe to settings stream, reload on app resume, use _settings.qrRefreshSeconds
   - Added WidgetsBindingObserver for lifecycle awareness
   - Methods panel now shows only enabled methods from settings

4. **Dashboard Quick Action Buttons**
   - Root cause: Buttons had TODO placeholders, no real navigation
   - Fix: Linked 'QR Code' to /attendance, 'Add Employee' to /employees/new

5. **EmployeeResolver Integration in Financial Shift**
   - Root cause: Financial shift screen could fail with NO_CONTEXT error
   - Fix: Use EmployeeResolverService.getEmployeeForUser() to guarantee employee
   - Only DB errors can now cause failure, not missing employee context
   - Added [EMPLOYEE_RESOLVED] logging

6. **Error Handling & UI Consistency**
   - Root cause: Silent failures, no retry options on error
   - Fix: Added _loadError state, error views with retry buttons
   - Dashboard, Financial Shift screens now show proper error panels

## Files Changed

- lib/core/services/settings_service.dart (lifecycle observer, reload methods)
- lib/presentation/screens/kiosk_screen.dart (barcode timer rebuild)
- lib/presentation/screens/attendance_screen.dart (settings reactivity)
- lib/presentation/screens/dashboard_screen.dart (button actions, error view)
- lib/presentation/screens/financial_shift_screen.dart (employee resolver, error view)

## Verification Checklist

- [ ] App runs without crashes
- [ ] Kiosk screen shows/hides QR based on settings
- [ ] Changing QR refresh interval rebuilds timer
- [ ] Settings changes reflect immediately in Kiosk
- [ ] Dashboard quick actions navigate correctly
- [ ] Financial shift opens without NO_CONTEXT error
- [ ] Error panels display with retry option
- [ ] No blank screens on data load failure
